jobDev.description: Hi I am Angel Niño Ortega, I seek to obtain a position as a Full Stack Web Developer in a company where I can maximize my skills in web development, leadership, and problem solving, and at the same time, contribute to the success of the company. I am also a self-taught programmer and I am always eager to learn new technologies and skills.
